info.name: compressbins
info.summary: Convert numpy bins to a string format ideal for creating frequency charts in the numpy-pandas ecosystem. Ex. [0, 2, 4, 6, 8, 10] -> ['0-2', '2-4', '4-6', '6-8', '8-10']
